[To find Laprida, go to http://www.fallingrain.com/world/AR/01/Laprida.html. A HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map can be accessed at http://healthmap.org/r/5KK9.

I fear that this will continue until the last owners of the local unvaccinated herds get around to terminating their procrastination and vaccinating their stock. Our heartfelt thanks to Ramon for keeping us updated on this emerging epidemic. - Mod.MHJ]
